title: (Thurs Full Show) Someone On The Show Pranked Another Show Member + Bobby's Crazy Day Yesterday + Ray Might Be Joining A Reality TV Show In A Different Country
itunes:title: (Thurs Full Show) Someone On The Show Pranked Another Show Member + Bobby's Crazy Day Yesterday + Ray Might Be Joining A Reality TV Show In A Different Country
description:
Lunchbox pranked Abby while they were in Vegas and it's either really mean or funny. Hear how the prank went down and how she got her revenge in-studio. Plus, Bobby had a crazy day yesterday that involved his dogs, execs in town, the Opry and tornado warnings... Then, a reality TV show that Ray has auditioned for multiple times is casting right now and he's thinking about trying to join it again but it's in a different country....

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
